<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200815/bfcd35d0fa2b4cb28081f95f20c093f6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不过这依然阻止不了拜仁的大杀特杀。比赛第63分钟，阿方索-戴维斯左边底线突入禁区，而后回传给基米希，后者前插轻松破门！5-2！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200815/f87eee2c1b7b421586725e0282aa8aae.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">随后主宰比赛的是拜仁的库蒂尼奥......上场后先助攻莱万破门，将比分改写为6-2！随后干脆自己操刀，连进2球！将比分锁定在8-2！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200815/f568f0a561ea464d8127409124c41f04.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200815/8b9caa1cebbb4913b6a1e3bc7781beb0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
